metadata.name: CyberCity Roles - Admin Intern
metadata.description: This unique NFT represents a specific profession in Cyber City. It features a custom-designed avatar that embodies the key characteristics and attributes of this profession. As an owner of this NFT, you'll be able to showcase your affinity for this profession and connect with like-minded individuals within the Cyber City Metaverse. You can also use it as your profile picture or digital identity across various platforms. As a holder, you would also have the ability to upgrade your avatar, as well as stake your avatar to claim Omnium Token (OTK), depending on the tier and amount of avatars you are holding.
